Remarks/Remarques: Curvve #6.00 is an clone of Curve #5.01 with some refinements throughout the entire range of the curve.  This is based on 3 open water measurements taken in 2023 along with 2022 mesurements which were shifted to last year until we could confirm change.
Curvve #5.01 is an exact clone of Curve #5.00 and was only created to extend the high end of existing curve due to major rain event on Feb 6th, 2022.
New curve 5.000 developed for 2017.  This was a result of 2017 measurements.  Slight changes on low end and medium to high end as well.
New curve using 2013 mm. Large scatter at bottom +/-11.6%
